      <title>摩根大通称印度必须修复经济管道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-24/india-has-to-fix-plumbing-of-economy-jpmorgan-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通首席印度经济学家 Sajjid Z. Chinoy 表示，印度政府必须找到除税收以外的新方法来创造收入来源。他在彭博特别网络研讨会上与彭博电视台的 Menaka Doshi 讨论了新的联邦预算（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-24/india-has-to-fix-plumbing-of-economy-jpmorgan-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 14:23:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑石抵押信托公司将股息削减 24%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-24/blackstone-mortgage-trust-cuts-dividend-by-24-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为商业房地产提供融资的黑石抵押贷款信托公司 (Blackstone Mortgage Trust Inc.) 正在削减 24% 的股息，因为违约率上升，借款人难以偿还贷款或再融资。彭博社观点栏目 (Bloomberg Opinion) 的 Nir ​​Kaissar 在“彭博公开利息” (Bloomberg Open Interest) 节目中进一步谈论了黑石的困境。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-24/blackstone-mortgage-trust-cuts-dividend-by-24-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 14:12:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>疲软数据增强美联储降息预期，美国国债收益率下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/treasury-yields-slide-as-weak-data-bolster-bets-on-fed-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场猜测美联储官员将很快下调美国利率，两年期美国国债收益率跌至二月份以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/treasury-yields-slide-as-weak-data-bolster-bets-on-fed-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 14:05:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
